{
  "id": "61e91b382199d5001d170277",
  "title": "(5.1.1.2) Let's practice",
  "created": 1554269493,
  "updated": 1554270196,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa2c",
      "text": "(5.1.1.2) Let's practice",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554270196,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa2d",
      "text": "Well, let's put the book aside and [practice] the [\"to write all out\" method] for 5 minutes. ",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269571,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa2e",
      "text": "If you have to write a report, choose it as the theme. If you do not have goals, use the theme \"if you tell others about this book, what do you tell?\"",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269493,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa2f",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269493,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa30",
      "text": " Prepare your favorite stationery to write.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa31",
      "text": " Set the timer to 5 minutes.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa32",
      "text": " Press the start button of the timer.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa33",
      "text": " Concentrate on the theme for 5 minutes.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269500,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa34",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269493,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa35",
      "text": "[If you have sufficient information in your mind, you feel 5 minutes very short. Most of time passes during you are writing.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269503,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa36",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554269505,
      "updated": 1554269505,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa37",
      "text": "On the other hand, if you do not have enough information in yourself, you feel 5 minutes very long.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269505,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa38",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269493,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa39",
      "text": "In the workshop I did (*), each participants was able to write 80 to 100 pieces in 16 minutes. So, on average we can write at a pace of 5 pieces per minute. That is 12 seconds per piece. Please do not feel this as pressure, and please play like a game aiming for high-score.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269512,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa3a",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554269517,
      "updated": 1554269517,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa3b",
      "text": "Note *3: This is a workshop held at [Kyoto University Summer Design School] in 2013 and 2014. On the theme of designing your way of learning, we spent 12 hours in 3 days for lectures, the practice of \"to write all out\" method, and then organize the pieces with [KJ method] to make a presentation.",
      "created": 1554269493,
      "updated": 1554269530,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066fa3c",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1554270196,
      "updated": 1554270196,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    }
  ]
}